{"tid":1064851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《哆啦A夢》道具成真？科學家宣稱研發「時光機」","createTime":"2019-03-16T23:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T21:39:37.000Z","uid":238973,"like":6,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9bec373c22eaa26be1aa9254117f1686dc32fc","tid":1064851,"uid":238973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:50:12.000Z","msg":"卡通《哆啦A夢》裡面的「時光機」現在可望成真，因為已經有俄羅斯科學家宣稱研發出「時光機器」，可以順利將「電子」回歸到上一個狀態，就像是「時間反轉」一樣，而且成功率還高達85%，想要「回到過去」尋找那些年的美好回憶，不是夢。<br />\n<br />\n大雄：「靜香不是會說謊的人，我要幫她找到證據，還她清白。」<br />\n<br />\n動畫《哆啦A夢》裡面的時光機或是經典科幻電影《回到未來》的「迪羅倫」飛天車，「時光旅行」現在可望成真。俄羅斯科學家宣稱已經製造出一台「時間機器」，可將微小粒子回溯到過去，也就是被打亂的「電子」，能回到先前的秩序，而且成功率高達85%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/15/1827617-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F15%2F1827617-XXL.jpg&h=a6cef0f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲《哆啦A夢》裡的時光機道具，可望在俄羅斯科學家的努力下成真。（圖／翻攝自dailymotion）<br />\n<br />\n拿撞球來做比喻，意思就是被撞開四散的球，能重新被拉回到原本的位置與狀態，就像是時間逆轉一樣。實驗結果一發布，立刻引發討論，因為要能讓「電子」被打散又自動回歸，已經挑戰了物理熱力學的第二定律。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/15/1827614-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F15%2F1827614-XXL.jpg&h=d1502202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲俄羅斯科學家宣稱已經製造出一台「時間機器」，而且成功率高達85%。（圖／翻攝自thesun）<br />\n<br />\n專家：「熱力學第二定律，說明熵和無序在封閉系統中會持續增加。」<br />\n<br />\n熱力學第二定律說明傳播過程的不可逆特性，但研究人員使用了量子電腦控制電子，才有辦法成功達到「時光倒轉」，如果換成一般情況，物體就不太可能主動「回歸」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/15/1827622-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F15%2F1827622-XXL.jpg&h=83a7eb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲時光機實驗結果一發布，立刻引發討論。（圖／翻攝自Weirdest News）<br />\n<br />\n原本遙不可及的「時光穿梭」幻想，現在指日可待，想要擁有可載人的「時光機」，不是夢。"},{"pid":"ea578998d951c996ca945cda6e7bd43fd39cde8d","tid":1064851,"uid":20849,"like":60,"dislike":115,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:53:56.000Z","msg":"留名睇廢老話唔識多啦a夢 只識叮噹"},{"pid":"5effcce5b48d72f71bcf4af2366afe7d5770a95e","tid":1064851,"uid":2419,"like":265,"dislike":37,"score":228,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"唔識多啦a夢 只識叮噹"},{"pid":"b5625da1a3d818f82fbaff4a979beb6b3085cbae","tid":1064851,"uid":40272,"like":119,"dislike":3,"score":116,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:55:23.000Z","msg":"即係屙舊屎淺起水花 <br />\n啲水花落返屎坑就係叫回到過去？"},{"pid":"e8116a260361ae2737a8351b2113a640efc05424","tid":1064851,"uid":36901,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:57:13.000Z","msg":"研究人員使用了量子電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52240579678ca218b6148d12c4cc683483f5f366","tid":1064851,"uid":186431,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ea578998d951c996ca945cda6e7bd43fd39cde8d","tid":1064851,"uid":20849,"like":60,"dislike":115,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:53:56.000Z","msg":"留名睇廢老話唔識多啦a夢 只識叮噹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:58:06.000Z","msg":"唔識多啦a夢 只識叮噹"},{"pid":"ef9fa2937ae2b834e28316925d452127e2ad3184","tid":1064851,"uid":153311,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:00:13.000Z","msg":"唔識多啦a夢 只識叮噹"},{"pid":"bd4d5bd906fc525dccb4093121459b87c2e1702c","tid":1064851,"uid":79355,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:01:29.000Z","msg":"唔識多啦a夢 只識叮噹"},{"pid":"1061fa9c9b494cc78e96a30d7af75aee0b6a65b9","tid":1064851,"uid":18913,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:03:33.000Z","msg":"唔識靜香 只識靜兒"},{"pid":"8d6bbebc255132308ad65d7dc553823c93e41799","tid":1064851,"uid":144843,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy