23:55:23.000Z","msg":"即係屙舊屎淺起水花 <br />\n啲水花落返屎坑就係叫回到過去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:53:30.000Z","msg":"錯 係淺完水花 理論上沒晒能量 但竟然無啦啦又有水花 所以話佢回到過去"},{"pid":"5792277f83324bc23300590c502c97ce8280f5b6","tid":1064851,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVUXqWp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVUXqWp.jpg&h=7da55285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b73a8d8010b1bc76432d9db4737a04a5a6ad22","tid":1064851,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"時光機係科學，行為是哲學!"},{"pid":"3c68e672faf04aec1db945455e98e36ec3539800","tid":1064851,"uid":205135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e8918bdeb6a5e103094dc021a3d677f3f772c29","tid":1064851,"uid":41655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"Steins;Gate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"D-mail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc360d9d23f6ecde97151e6a8e42951ac61405fd","tid":1064851,"uid":138476,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"上連登 勿9up<br />\n熱力學第二定律講嘅熵，係指物件嘅不規律程度會不斷增加。例如你大力開一局桌球，你好難會見到堆波撞開之後彈幾下牆又返返去原本整齊排三角形嘅狀態，原因純粹就係統計學上啲波隨機擺嘅情況下咁啱堆波砌出一個整齊三角形嘅機率極微細，你只會見到佢哋越來越亂<br />\n<br />\n文章講嘅電子「自動」返返去低熵嘅狀態就係屬於違反第二定律嘅狀況，啫係時光倒流<br />\n<br />\n至於點解物件嘅排列狀態同時間有關？就係因為我地對時間嘅理解就係基於熵嘅增加本身。例如聽朝起身睇新聞見到又有人墮樓，由低熵嘅高位能狀態去到砰一聲，地面同埋空氣粒子受碰撞而加熱隨機移動嘅高熵高熱能狀態 你就知道「唉！又開始新一日」咁如果有一日地面嘅熱能自動減少，受害者飛返上天台，你咪可以話時間逆轉咗囉，之不過呢件事發生嘅機率無限貼近零，大概宇宙大爆炸到依家都未發生過一次<br />\n<br />\n咁我手動將啲亂咗嘅檯波排返個三角形出嚟係咪啫係減少咗熵？個個都可以成為逆轉時間嘅超人？咪傻啦梗係唔得！原因就係你郁動緊肌肉排波嘅時候係用緊糖分入面嘅化學能，最終散熱嗰陣加熱咗空氣等空氣粒子郁得更加亂，而你用力排波所增加嘅熵一定會俾啲波減少咗嘅熵多。結論就係呀婆化妝唔算逆轉時間<br />\n<br />\n至少篇報導無前後矛盾，只係班媒體左cop右cop寫咗篇殘障嘅文章出嚟，出名醒目嘅連登仔自然會出嚟圍爐控訴個研究喺度9up"},{"pid":"a1c238094ec7e82fef2e5ff5a8fa1f92ae097925","tid":1064851,"uid":40644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5792277f83324bc23300590c502c97ce8280f5b6","tid":1064851,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVUXqWp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVUXqWp.jpg&h=7da55285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:47:59.000Z","msg":"洗咩研發時光機姐<br />\n明明都有人入到量子領域啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5f46813c3d30f15819ad67255518fadc04bce5","tid":1064851,"uid":60133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26910c91c5e3dd1268f5e1cd7907a02fb7c76d06","tid":1064851,"uid":46408,"like":144,"dislike":0,"score":144,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.izismile.com/img/img4/20110118/640/daily_picdump_594_640_high_22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.izismile.com%2Fimg%2Fimg4%2F20110118%2F640%2Fdaily_picdump_594_640_high_22.jpg&h=2078f2a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:01:55.000Z","msg":"望到個title第一時間就諗到呢個漫畫"},{"pid":"eab9709f34bc2f256748aeae7fd1900887a03009","tid":1064851,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"唔信"},{"pid":"b53f2b6513d18ad6754c4d37c0df16b463c64374","tid":1064851,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEOhra5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEOhra5.jpg&h=df36d36d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f35b39e94bd60f4309a252e060a20c681f8fa11a","tid":1064851,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5625da1a3d818f82fbaff4a979beb6b3085cbae","tid":1064851,"uid":40272,"like":119,"dislike":